        "content": "**Paging SLOs (Phase 1):** page only on `outcome=exhausted`, pusher degraded-session ratio. `outcome=recovered` heals are dashboard-only — do not page.\n\n**Noise budget:** ≤2 new PAGE alerts in the first 2 weeks after deploy (pusher degraded ratio). Sync enqueue_failed PAGE is paused until Cloud Run custom metrics reach Prometheus — use Cloud Logging meanwhile (see sync-dispatch runbook). LLM gateway fallback is ticket-tier.\n\nRunbooks: `backend/docs/runbooks/resilience-dashboards.md`.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "12.1.0",
      "title": "Alerting & noise budget",
      "type": "text"
    },
