      "title": "Sync dispatch — enqueue_failed share (PAGE SLO)",
      "description": "**Scrape gap:** Metric definitions and emit sites live in-repo (`utils/metrics.py` + `routers/sync.py` on Cloud Run `backend-sync`), but GKE Prometheus only scrapes backend-listen and pusher — so this panel may be empty until Cloud Run custom metrics are exported. Until then, use Cloud Logging for `omi_fallback_event component=sync_dispatch reason=enqueue_failed`. PAGE alert is paused.",
